posting_body: ['Schedule a Tour Today: <URL>', 'Surround yourself with comfort and convenience at our luxury apartments in Stockbridge, GA.', 'Southwinds Point has a variety of one bedroom, two bedroom, and three bedroom apartments in Stockbridge, GA with amazing amenities.', 'Each home has elegant details like crown molding, custom light fixtures, custom cabinetry, and plantation-style window treatments.', 'Our apartments near Atlanta are also spacious enough to accommodate an in-unit washer and dryer, additional storage, and there are even roommate style floorplans available.', 'Residents of our gated community have exclusive access to our fitness gym, tennis court, resort style pool, coffee bar, and so much more!', 'Southwinds Point also brings residents close to notable attractions in Henry County like Heritage Park, Atlanta Motor Speedway, and Panola Mountain State Park.', 'Amenities:', '-Spacious Living Rooms', '-Additional Storage', '-Resort-style Swimming Pool', '-Fun in the Sun Playground', '-Large Kitchens', '-Covered Private Patios and Balconies', '-Hard Surface Floors', '-Stainless Steel Appliances', '-Private Dining Area', '-Internet Cafe', '-Subway Tile Backsplash', '-Clubroom w/ Billiards', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'Equal Housing Opportunity', 'Pricing and availability are subject to change.']
